<Verbatim PAsource="" >A battle for compensation by an English couple who claimed they were victims of racial discrimination </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >while </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >living in a Scottish village ended </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >yesterday </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >when lawyers reached an out-of-court settlement. </Verbatim>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Frank Walters, 52, and his wife Sandra, 53, said they had been vindicated with the undisclosed settlement, believed to be in the region £4,000 plus costs estimated at £40,000.</Verbatim>


